    <briefdescription>
<para>Used for displaying native images. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1NativeImage" kindref="compound">NativeImage</ref> can be created internally or externally by native image. <ref refid="classDali_1_1NativeImage" kindref="compound">NativeImage</ref> is a platform specific way of providing pixel data to the GPU for rendering, for example via an EGL image.</para>
<para>@SINCE_1_1.4 <simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classDali_1_1NativeImage" kindref="compound">NativeImage</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
